{"tid":1378500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷工勝利方程式] 8月5日全港大罷工將會大成功！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:01:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:19:19.000Z","uid":167548,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b4f621adfdaa8b20b7e23bda9f9e30e77df44289","tid":1378500,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:01:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7月29日至8月2日起全港地鐵站出入口設置聯署簽名站，</span><br />\n或者集中係中環遮打舉行簽名晚會。<br />\n聯署者並不需要提供自身性名,<br />\n但必需提供個人行業, 最好是自身公司名稱。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8月3日至8月4日舉行全面和理非大遊行並由民陣舉辦。</span><br />\n在遊行路線設置大量街站。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">8月5日正式啟動全港性無限期大罷工！</span></span>"},{"pid":"ccce6102f6501c67baa3310c892d30d4b6750ab9","tid":1378500,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8018dc9b7b4473c538cb03d5229fcabc7e5e679d","tid":1378500,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:02:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b39dd138887697e8edb0a3ed8a52370e419b0eae","tid":1378500,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:02:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5365e819119718e4deef8809685ee3ab54cc925b","tid":1378500,"uid":127331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6bab82ebc5c8259ae834fa73f7a7ac633da30d41","tid":1378500,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cfdf76f9df235a2746b404d90ba53e80b3d64b1","tid":1378500,"uid":127331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"p